---------------------------------------------------------
[spell]: Animate Dead
[level]: 5th Lvl Necromancy
[cost] : 65 sp + Corpse
[type] : none
[delay]: none
---------------------------------------------------------
The sinister Animate Dead corpse will magically restore
some life to a corpse so that it will assist you in
battle.  The mindless corpse can only attack one target
and will fight until destroyed.  Only the most evil of
Mages can use this spell.
---------------------------------------------------------

